      <title>大众汽车预计2024年销量增长将放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volkswagen-expects-sales-growth-slow-2024-2024-03-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲顶级汽车制造商大众汽车周五表示，预计 2024 年销量增长将较去年放缓，理由是竞争加剧、排放监管更严格以及原材料和能源价格上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volkswagen-expects-sales-growth-slow-2024-2024-03-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Mar 2024 14:26:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
